            <h2> What is GameWell ? </h2>
            <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
                <p>
                    GameWell is an online bank of games that are designed for people with dementia. The games exercise the players minds by engaging their attention, perception, and memory, as well as their problem solving, planning, reasoning, and decision making skills. The games are cooperative, meaning that players cannot lose or make errors. Instead the game tasks can be completed as many times as necessary to accomplish the game and players can aim for accuracy.
                    GameWell is best played alongside friends and family, therefore the games are appropriate for people of all ages. The more often the games are played the better the patients health and wellbeing. So, it was a priority for the website to be fun and enjoyable for players including features such as customizable avatars and real-world rewards for playing frequently.
                </p>
